long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Remember your tabs everywhere!

TabsManagement is a tool to help you organize your tabs and windows in the browser. Your sessions are saved to the cloud, so you have access to them on any computer.

The sessions are saved to a GoogleSheets file on your GoogleDrive, so, to start using this extension, you will have to grant some authorizations to an AppScript.

This project is open-source! You can check the source code here:
https://gitlab.com/LeonardoSirino/TabsManagement
